data.description: Terrific Tatum Ranch Tri-Level now available!  The stunning rear yard is a private desert oasis, featuring a Pebble Tech self-cleaning diving pool w/ water feature, spacious covered patio, firepit & built in grill & view fence! Over 3,350 square feet featuring 5 large bedrooms PLUS bonus room & 3 full baths w/ dual sinks!  Open living/dining room entry with vaulted ceilings & lots of bright natural light; family room w/ recessed lighting, fireplace and under-stairs storage; updated kitchen w/ island, stainless steel appliances & loads of cabinets; primary suite with double door entry, vaulted ceilings, en suite bath with separate tub/tile shower, walk-in closet & private deck and more to see! Great Tatum Ranch location close to Cave Creek/Carefree, Desert Ridge, golf, shopping and more!!
